content: This documentation records some common questions and answers, mainly from GitHub Discussions. How to switch Hugo environments? Default environments are development with hugo server and production with hugo. Due to limitations in the local development environment, the comment system, CDN and fingerprint will not be enabled in the development environment. You could enable these features with hugo server -e production. Question Question Didn’t find your questions? Join the discussions.

content: Add your FixIt site You could add your FixIt site to this page in nickname lexicographical order via making a PR or editing data , the format is as follows: - nickname: <your nickname> avatar: <your avatar> url: <your site link> description: <description of your site>  Website failure, stop maintenance and improper content may be unlinked!
